T1  - 2018 KLEIN LECTURE: INDIVIDUAL AND AGGREGATE LABOR SUPPLY IN HETEROGENEOUS AGENT ECONOMIES WITH INTENSIVE AND EXTENSIVE MARGINS
AU  - Chang, Yongsung
AU  - Kim, Sun-Bin
AU  - Kwon, Kyooho
AU  - Rogerson, Richard
