T1  - UNDERSTANDING PER-CAPITA INCOME GROWTH IN PREINDUSTRIAL EUROPE
AU  - Lagerlöf, Nils-Petter
Y1  - 2019/02/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12350
T2  - International Economic Review
